  <brief_title>Evaluation of Platelet Rich Fibrin on Reduction of Periodontal Problems After Surgical Removal of Mandibular Third Molar</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of Platelet Rich Fibrin Efficacy on Reduction of Periodontal Problems</official_title>
  <sponsors>
